  "message": "test(conformance): add MEMORY USAGE and MALLOC-STATS tests\n\nAdd 6 new conformance cases for MEMORY subcommands:\n- MEMORY USAGE on existing key (returns integer bytes)\n- MEMORY USAGE on nonexistent key (returns null)\n- MEMORY USAGE with SAMPLES option\n- MEMORY MALLOC-STATS (returns allocator message)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
